<Layout title="Colecciones | AETHERIA" description="Descubra la colección completa de AETHERIA. Extraits de parfum, ediciones limitadas y aromas de autor. Obras maestras olfativas para los conocedores.">
  <header
    data-mobile-nav
    class="sticky top-0 w-full z-50 flex justify-between items-center h-[100px] px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop bg-background/90 backdrop-blur-xl border-b border-outline-variant"
  >
    <div class="flex items-center gap-12">
      <h1 class="font-display-xl text-headline-md tracking-widest text-primary">
        <a href="/">AETHERIA</a>
      </h1>
      <nav class="hidden md:flex gap-8">
        <a
          class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-primary border-b border-primary pb-1 transition-colors duration-300"
          href="/collections"
        >Colecciones</a
        >
        <a
          class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-300"
          href="#"
        >Notas de Aroma</a
        >
        <a
          class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-300"
          href="#"
        >El Archivo</a
        >
        <a
          class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-300"
          href="#"
        >A Medida</a
        >
      </nav>
    </div>
    <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
      <div class="hidden lg:flex items-center border-b border-outline py-1 px-2 gap-2">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">search</span>
        <input
          class="bg-transparent border-none focus:ring-0 text-[10px] font-label-caps tracking-widest p-0 w-32"
          placeholder="BUSCAR AROMAS"
          type="text"
        />
      </div>
      <button class="touch-target hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-2xl">person</span>
      </button>
      <button class="touch-target hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-2xl">shopping_bag</span>
      </button>
      <button class="hamburger md:hidden touch-target" data-toggle-mobile aria-label="Menú">
        <span></span>
        <span></span>
        <span></span>
      </button>
    </div>
  </header>
  <div class="mobile-drawer" data-mobile-drawer>
    <a href="/collections" class="font-label-caps text-lg tracking-widest text-primary hover:opacity-60 transition-opacity">Colecciones</a>
    <a href="#" class="font-label-caps text-lg tracking-widest text-primary hover:opacity-60 transition-opacity">Notas de Aroma</a>
    <a href="#" class="font-label-caps text-lg tracking-widest text-primary hover:opacity-60 transition-opacity">El Archivo</a>
    <a href="#" class="font-label-caps text-lg tracking-widest text-primary hover:opacity-60 transition-opacity">A Medida</a>
    <hr class="border-outline-variant my-4" />
    <a href="/" class="font-body-md text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors">Inicio</a>
  </div>
  <div class="mobile-overlay" data-mobile-overlay></div>
  <main class="min-h-screen">
    <section class="pt-28 pb-12 px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop text-center md:text-left">
      <h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg mb-4">La Colección</h2>
      <p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl">
        Descubra nuestro archivo curado de obras maestras olfativas. Cada
        fragancia es una narrativa contada a través de los botánicos más
        preciosos y resinas raras del mundo.
      </p>
    </section>
    <!-- Filter Bar -->
    <section
      class="sticky top-[100px] bg-background z-40 border-y border-outline-variant px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop py-6"
    >
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between overflow-x-auto gap-8">
        <div class="flex gap-10 items-center whitespace-nowrap">
          <button
            class="font-label-caps text-label-caps border-b-2 border-primary pb-1"
          >Todo</button>
          <button
            class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors"
          >Floral</button>
          <button
            class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors"
          >Amaderado</button>
          <button
            class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors"
          >Oriental</button>
          <button
            class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors"
          >Cítrico</button>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-on-surface-variant"
          >Ordenar por:</span
          >
          <button
            class="font-label-caps text-label-caps flex items-center gap-1"
          >
            Más nuevo
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">expand_more</span>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <!-- Product Grid -->
    <section class="py-16 px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop">
      <div
        class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 xl:grid-cols-4 gap-x-gutter gap-y-16"
      >
        {products.map((product) => (
          <div class="group cursor-pointer">
            <div
              class="aspect-[3/4] bg-surface-container-low relative overflow-hidden mb-6 flex items-center justify-center p-8"
            >
              <img
                alt={product.name}
                class="w-full h-full object-contain transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105"
                src={product.img}
              />
              <div
                class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary/5 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"
              ></div>
              <button
                class="absolute bottom-6 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-primary text-on-primary font-label-caps text-[10px] py-3 px-8 translate-y-10 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform duration-300 max-md:translate-y-0"
              >
                AÑADIR RÁPIDO
              </button>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <p
                class="font-label-caps text-[10px] tracking-widest text-on-surface-variant mb-1 uppercase"
              >
                {product.category}
              </p>
              <h3
                class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm mb-2 group-hover:italic transition-all"
              >
                {product.name}
              </h3>
              <p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-primary">
                {product.price}
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>
    <!-- Newsletter -->
    <section class="py-section-gap px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop bg-surface-container-low">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg mb-8">
          La Esencia del Tiempo
        </h2>
        <p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg mb-12 leading-relaxed">
          Suscríbase a nuestro archivo privado para obtener acceso temprano a
          lanzamientos de lotes limitados, consultas de aromas a medida y
          narrativas sensoriales de nuestros Maestros Perfumistas.
        </p>
        <form class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 max-w-lg mx-auto">
          <input
            class="flex-grow bg-transparent border-b border-primary py-3 px-0 font-label-caps text-[10px] focus:ring-0 focus:border-tertiary-container transition-all"
            placeholder="CORREO ELECTRÓNICO"
            type="email"
          />
          <button
            class="bg-primary text-on-primary font-label-caps text-[10px] tracking-widest py-4 px-10 hover:bg-tertiary transition-all duration-300"
          >
            SUSCRIBIRSE
          </button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
